Qatar Airways to operate repatriation flights from Doha to Europe as air traffic stays shut","native":"Qatar Airways to operate repatriation flights from Doha to Europe as air traffic stays shut","published":true,"updated_time":"2026-03-06T23:34:47.959Z","published_time":"2026-03-06T23:33:50.455Z","article_type":"Standard","display_my_news":true,"display_newsletter_signup":true,"display_notifications":true,"display_related_media":true,"display_related_organizations":true,"content_code":"metered","source":{"name":"Reuters","original_name":"Reuters"},"company_rics":"AC.TO,DAL.N","title":"Qatar Airways to operate repatriation flights from Doha to Europe as air traffic stays shut","basic_headline":"Qatar Airways to operate repatriation flights from Doha to Europe as air traffic stays shut","distributor":"Reuters","description":"Qatar Airways plans to operate a few repatriation flights from Doha to Europe on Saturday, but commercial flights remained suspended as the U.S.-Israel war on Iran has forced the closure ​of Qatari airspace since last week.","primary_media_type":"image","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"RULES:IRAN","description":"RULES:IRAN","slug":"rules-iran","text":"RULES:IRAN","topic_url":"/tags/rules-iran/"},"word_count":571,"read_minutes":3,"kicker":{"name":"Middle East","path":"/world/middle-east/","names":["World","Middle East"]},"ad_topics":["DeathInjrConft","trans","DeathInjrConft"],"thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/42LH5PSZ5ROLVN3OC6WC2ILBN4.jpg","caption":"A Qatar Airways plane sits on the tarmac at Los Angeles International Airport (LAX) in Los Angeles, California, U.S. March 3, 2026. REUTERS/Daniel Cole","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/42LH5PSZ5ROLVN3OC6WC2ILBN4.jpg?auth=a3f55ecc4954414c66febdba852a3b48accbf63f69574c68d6ada3527f9c85d5","location":"Los Angeles, CA, United States","id":"42LH5PSZ5ROLVN3OC6WC2ILBN4","authors":"Daniel Cole","alt_text":"A Qatar Airways plane sits on the tarmac at Los Angeles International Airport (LAX)","width":6500,"height":4335,"subtitle":"A Qatar Airways plane sits on the tarmac at Los Angeles International Airport (LAX)","slug":"IRAN-CRISIS-AIRLINES-CARGO","updated_at":"2026-03-06T23:34:00Z","company":"Reuters","purchase_licensing_path":"https://www.reutersconnect.com/item/a-qatar-airways-plane-sits-on-the-tarmac-at-los-angeles-international-airport-lax/dGFnOnJldXRlcnMuY29tLDIwMjY6bmV3c21sX1JDMjZYSkE1TjFQUA%3D%3D/?utm_medium=rcom-article-media&utm_campaign=rcom-rcp-lead"},"display_time":"2026-03-06T23:33:50.455Z","authors":[{"id":"parth.chandna@thomsonreuters.com","name":"Parth Chandna","first_name":"Parth","last_name":"Chandna","company":"Reuters","thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/H24NV3AFCZCWPC463OG3JRYY7U.jpg","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com%2Freuters%2FH24NV3AFCZCWPC463OG3JRYY7U.jpg?auth=4dd3566d980534ddab2fb815cfdf9f08e04ca3d4f4dd0c88f6e42931b1e77167"},"social_links":[{"site":"email","url":"mailto:Parth.Chandna@thomsonreuters.com"}],"byline":"Parth Chandna","topic_url":"/authors/parth-chandna/"}]},{"id":"E3F73AUODZM27HZNB5KQUXXG6M","revision_id":"LBMR42QPFBCEZNK5CA6UCB5A4A","canonical_url":"/world/middle-east/iran-spent-years-fostering-proxies-iraq-now-many-arent-eager-join-war-2026-03-06/","website":"reuters","web":"Iran fostered its Iraqi proxies for years. Now, few are in the fight","native":"Iran spent years fostering proxies in Iraq. Now, many aren’t eager to join the war","headline_feature":"EXCLUSIVE","published":true,"updated_time":"2026-03-06T13:33:31.790Z","published_time":"2026-03-06T13:32:13.088Z","article_type":"Standard","display_my_news":true,"display_newsletter_signup":true,"display_notifications":true,"display_related_media":true,"display_related_organizations":true,"content_code":"metered","source":{"name":"Reuters","original_name":"Reuters"},"title":"Exclusive: Iran spent years fostering proxies in Iraq. Now, many aren’t eager to join the war","basic_headline":"Exclusive: Iran spent years fostering proxies in Iraq. Now, many aren’t eager to join the war","distributor":"Reuters","description":"Iran has spent decades and billions of dollars preparing foreign proxy fighters like A.J., a commander in a pro-Iranian paramilitary group in Iraq, for a moment just like this. Since the U.S. and Israel went to war on the Islamic Republic a week ago, A.J. has been awaiting marching orders from Tehran.","primary_media_type":"image","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"RULES:IRAN","description":"RULES:IRAN","slug":"rules-iran","text":"RULES:IRAN","topic_url":"/tags/rules-iran/"},"word_count":3524,"read_minutes":18,"kicker":{"name":"Middle East","path":"/world/middle-east/","names":["World","Middle East"]},"ad_topics":["DeathInjrConft","pol","DeathInjrConft"],"thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU.jpg","caption":"Birds fly as smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, amid the U.S.-Israel conflict with Iran, in Tehran, Iran, March 2, 2026. WANA (West Asia News Agency) via REUTERS/File Photo","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU.jpg?auth=7652ca47e203e069f21cc0935d308394bed143e687f52757889c85c989390a0f","location":"Tehran, IRAN","id":"QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU","authors":"Wana News Agency","alt_text":"Smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, in Tehran","width":5500,"height":3666,"subtitle":"Smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, in Tehran","slug":"IRAN-CRISIS-IRAQ-PROXIES","updated_at":"2026-03-06T13:33:18Z","company":"Reuters","purchase_licensing_path":"https://www.reutersconnect.com/item/smoke-rises-following-an-explosion-after-israel-and-the-us-launched-strikes-on-