ges from the latest in nuclear power, to environment regulations, to U.S. sanctions and geopolitics. He has been a member of three teams in the past two years that have won Reuters best journalism of the year awards.  As a cyclist he is happiest outside.","topic_url":"/authors/timothy-gardner/","role":"Energy and Environment Correspondent"}]},{"id":"Z3T6GIIEBNJGFOXD4SAVA2DPEY","revision_id":"PTAZVUTD7JGDXERTM4GQO5LTBQ","canonical_url":"/world/middle-east/israeli-military-says-unintentionally-struck-un-agency-truck-gaza-2026-03-06/","website":"reuters","web":"Israeli military says unintentionally struck UN agency truck in Gaza","native":"Israeli military says unintentionally struck UN agency truck in Gaza","published":true,"updated_time":"2026-03-06T20:13:23.582Z","published_time":"2026-03-06T20:13:16.748Z","article_type":"Standard","display_my_news":true,"display_newsletter_signup":true,"display_notifications":true,"display_related_media":true,"display_related_organizations":true,"content_code":"metered","source":{"name":"Reuters","original_name":"Reuters"},"title":"Israeli military says unintentionally struck UN agency truck in Gaza","basic_headline":"Israeli military says unintentionally struck UN agency truck in Gaza","distributor":"Reuters","description":"Israel's military said on Friday that a \"firing component\" launched by its navy unintentionally struck a fuel ​truck belonging to a United Nations agency in Gaza ‌the previous day, an incident that prompted the agency to publicly call for a full investigation.","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"Israel and Hamas at War","description":"Israel and Hamas at War","slug":"rules-israel-palestinians","text":"RULES:ISRAEL-PALESTINIANS","can_follow":true,"topic_url":"/world/israel-hama-at-war/"},"word_count":294,"read_minutes":2,"kicker":{"name":"Middle East","path":"/world/middle-east/","names":["World","Middle East"]},"ad_topics":["DeathInjrConft","pol","DeathInjrConft"],"display_time":"2026-03-06T20:13:16.748Z","authors":