:"podcastslogo"},"node_type":"section"},{"id":"/podcasts/reuters-econ-world/","website":"reuters","name":"Reuters Econ World","description":"Join Reuters journalist Carmel Crimmins every week as she and her guests pick apart a key economic principle behind the world’s news. Get beyond buzzwords and technical terms to understand the ideas and debates shaping the global economic agenda.","page_title":"Reuters Econ World","language":"en","template_type":"section","network_id":"7d3db05a-8c41-11ed-a109-9b062d29da32","podcast_id":"3c37d102-0c70-11ef-9f2a-d3c80df1fc79","type":"section","advertising":{"sponsored":"false","sponsor_logo_type":"podcastslogo"},"node_type":"section"},{"id":"/podcasts/on-assignment/","website":"reuters","name":"On Assignment","description":"Dive into the stories behind the news with a new podcast from Reuters. We take you past the headlines right to the heart of the action. From the frontlines of war to corporate boardrooms and the centers of political power, listen to our award-winning investigative journalists around the world make sense of the most important stories today.","page_title":"On Assignment","language":"en","template_type":"section","network_id":"7d3db05a-8c41-11ed-a109-9b062d29da32","podcast_id":"e3c7d1b2-8c45-11ed-80a2-172771c99810","type":"section","advertising":{"sponsored":"false","sponsor_logo_type":"podcastslogo"},"node_type":"section"},{"id":"/podcasts/viewsroom/","website":"reuters","name":"Viewsroom","description":"Pull up a chair and join the debate about the biggest stories in global business and finance. Breakingviews columnists talk about the big numbers, crunchy deals and nasty spats in global business and economics, offering a weekly dose of financial insight that goes beyond the concise and provocative views readers get from our columns every day.","page_title":"Viewsroom","language":"en","template_type":"section","network_id":"aa71465a-a087-11ec-8680-73c03cf16654","podcast_id":"3f585882-b431-11ec-b607-27400e0231df"