rael backing Iranian Kurdish plans to seize Iran border areas, sources say","headline_feature":"EXCLUSIVE","published":true,"updated_time":"2026-03-06T17:42:47.828Z","published_time":"2026-03-06T17:34:10.579Z","article_type":"Standard","display_my_news":true,"display_newsletter_signup":true,"display_notifications":true,"display_related_media":true,"display_related_organizations":true,"content_code":"metered","source":{"name":"Reuters","original_name":"Reuters"},"title":"Exclusive: Israel backing Iranian Kurdish plans to seize Iran border areas, sources say","basic_headline":"Exclusive: Israel backing Iranian Kurdish plans to seize Iran border areas, sources say","distributor":"Reuters","description":"Israel has been bombing parts of western Iran to support Iranian Kurdish militias who hope to exploit the U.S.-Israeli war on Iran to seize towns near the frontier, ​according to three sources familiar with Israel's talks with the factions.","primary_media_type":"gallery","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"RULES:IRAN","description":"RULES:IRAN","slug":"rules-iran","text":"RULES:IRAN","topic_url":"/tags/rules-iran/"},"word_count":1025,"read_minutes":6,"kicker":{"name":"Middle East","path":"/world/middle-east/","names":["World","Middle East"]},"ad_topics":["DeathInjrConft","pol","DeathInjrConft"],"thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/P4REZ6DJYFPVVKDV7G46KDK75Y.jpg","caption":"Smoke rises following an explosion, amid the U.S.-Israeli conflict with Iran, in Tehran, Iran, March 6, 2026. Stringer/WANA (West Asia News Agency) via REUTERS","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/P4REZ6DJYFPVVKDV7G46KDK75Y.jpg?auth=e3322a7d2092103a0513dad2d030daa4c59a6f60664198b8cf3a10c1d9d0dd7e","location":"TEHRAN, IRAN","id":"P4REZ6DJYFPVVKDV7G46KDK75Y","authors":"Stringer","alt_text":"Smoke rises following an explosion, amid the U.S.-Israeli conflict with Iran, in Tehran","width":5192,"height":3462,"subtitle":"Smoke rises following