ment just like this. Since the U.S. and Israel went to war on the Islamic Republic a week ago, A.J. has been awaiting marching orders from Tehran.","primary_media_type":"image","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"RULES:IRAN","description":"RULES:IRAN","slug":"rules-iran","text":"RULES:IRAN","topic_url":"/tags/rules-iran/"},"word_count":3524,"read_minutes":18,"kicker":{"name":"Middle East","path":"/world/middle-east/","names":["World","Middle East"]},"ad_topics":["DeathInjrConft","pol","DeathInjrConft"],"thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU.jpg","caption":"Birds fly as smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, amid the U.S.-Israel conflict with Iran, in Tehran, Iran, March 2, 2026. WANA (West Asia News Agency) via REUTERS/File Photo","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU.jpg?auth=7652ca47e203e069f21cc0935d308394bed143e687f52757889c85c989390a0f","location":"Tehran, IRAN","id":"QVWH3EMQ2JKJLKCJRQ3GPCI2GU","authors":"Wana News Agency","alt_text":"Smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, in Tehran","width":5500,"height":3666,"subtitle":"Smoke rises following an explosion, after Israel and the U.S. launched strikes on Iran, in Tehran","slug":"IRAN-CRISIS-IRAQ-PROXIES","updated_at":"2026-03-06T13:33:18Z","company":"Reuters","purchase_licensing_path":"https://www.reutersconnect.com/item/smoke-rises-following-an-explosion-after-israel-and-the-us-launched-strikes-on-iran-in-tehran/dGFnOnJldXRlcnMuY29tLDIwMjY6bmV3c21sX1JDMkVXSkFNSDhRRg%3D%3D/?utm_medium=rcom-article-media&utm_campaign=rcom-rcp-lead"},"authors":[{"id":"john.davison@thomsonreuters.com","name":"John Davison","first_name":"John","last_name":"Davison","company":"Reuters","thumbnail":{"url":"https://author-service-images-prod-us-east-1.publishing.aws.arc.pub/reuters/64653978-5185-4773-a354-aa7316b8b432.JPG","t