-sends-shockwaves-through-global-business-2026-03-06/","website":"reuters","web":"US-Israel war with Iran sends shockwaves through global business","native":"US-Israel war with Iran sends shockwaves through global business","published":true,"updated_time":"2026-03-06T20:35:48.120Z","published_time":"2026-03-06T18:09:08.414Z","article_type":"Standard","display_my_news":true,"display_newsletter_signup":true,"display_notifications":true,"display_related_media":true,"display_related_organizations":true,"content_code":"metered","source":{"name":"Reuters","original_name":"Reuters"},"company_rics":"000660.KS,2317.TW,2330.TW,ALBH.BH,AMZN.O,CPRI.MI,INCH.L,MS.N,NVDA.O,RKT.L,RWEG.DE,SN.L,VTYV.L,WIZZ.L","title":"US-Israel war with Iran sends shockwaves through global business","basic_headline":"US-Israel war with Iran sends shockwaves through global business","distributor":"Reuters","description":"The U.S.-Israeli war with Iran is rattling businesses worldwide, driving up energy prices, squeezing supplies of critical raw materials and raising questions about the reliability of trade routes critical to the flow ​of goods from food to car parts.","primary_media_type":"gallery","primary_tag":{"short_bio":"Medtech","description":"Medtech","slug":"rhpi-medtech","text":"RHPI:MEDTECH","is_topic":true,"can_follow":true,"topic_url":"/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/medtech/"},"word_count":1263,"read_minutes":7,"kicker":{"name":"World","path":"/world/","names":["World","Europe"]},"ad_topics":["auto","DeathInjrConft","econ","hlthcr","hsing","ivbk","pol","tech","trade","trans","DeathInjrConft"],"thumbnail":{"url":"https://cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/F7WXB6OWHBLKNBQFVKFFDOQA2Y.jpg","caption":"Smoke rises following an explosion, amid the U.S.-Israeli conflict with Iran, in Tehran, Iran, March 5, 2026. Majid Asgaripour/WANA (West Asia News Agency) via REUTERS","type":"image","resizer_url":"https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/F7WXB6OWHBLKNBQFVKFFDOQA2Y.jpg?auth=4cf